) }; }; const mapStateToProps = (state) => { return { squat: state.maxes.squat, bench: state.maxes.bench, deadlift: state.maxes.deadlift, ohp: state.maxes.ohp, powerclean: state.maxes.powerclean, squatIncrement: state.maxes.squatIncrement, benchIncrement: state.maxes.benchIncrement, deadliftIncrement: state.maxes.deadliftIncrement, ohpIncrement: state.maxes.ohpIncrement, powercleanIncrement: state.maxes.powercleanIncrement } } export default connect(mapStateToProps)(StartingStrength);
